'''Stripe'''是一家提供讓個人或公司在[[互聯網|互聯網]]上接受付款服務的[[支付服务提供商|支付服务提供商]]。Stripe提供在網上接受付款所需的技術、避免{{le|信用卡詐騙|Credit card fraud}}技術及銀行基礎設施<ref>{{cite news|work=CNBC|url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/102655071|title=Stripe|accessdate=2016-01-07|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702095221/http://www.cnbc.com/id/102655071|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 付款後勤 ==

[[網頁開發者|網頁開發者]]可以使用Stripe在無需開設{{le|商家帳戶|Merchant Account}}下在網上接受付款<ref>{{cite web|last = Carr|first = Austin|title = Inside Stripe, The Paypal Competitor Backed By Paypal Founders Peter Thiel, Elon Musk|url = http://www.fastcompany.com/1813087/inside-stripe-paypal-competitor-backed-paypal-founders-peter-thiel-elon-musk|work = FastCompany|accessdate = 2014-04-02|date = 2012-02-01|archive-date = 2020-04-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200423152436/https://www.fastcompany.com/1813087/inside-stripe-paypal-competitor-backed-paypal-founders-peter-thiel-elon-musk|dead-url = no}}</ref>。Stripe在付款後兩天內等候期檢查交易所涉及的公司以防止潛在的詐騙，然後Stripe便會把資金傳送到收款人的戶口<ref name="Startup Grind">{{cite web|title = The Collison Brothers and Story Behind The Founding Of Stripe|url = http://startupgrind.com/2012/02/true-startup-story-the-collison-brothers-and-stripe-com/|work = Startup Grind|accessdate = 2014-04-02|date = 2012-02-09|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407071804/http://startupgrind.com/2012/02/true-startup-story-the-collison-brothers-and-stripe-com/|archivedate = 2014-04-07}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==

{{le|帕特里克·科里森|Patrick Collison}}和{{le|約翰·科里森|John Collison}}在2010年成立了Stripe<ref name="Startup Grind"/>，該[[創始公司|創始公司]]初期名叫「/dev/payments」。這個名字在公司外經常被人拼錯造成了混淆，所以便改名為「Stripe」<ref>{{cite web|last = Brockman|first = Greg|title = How Did Stripe Come Up With Its Name?|url = http://www.forbes.com/sites/quora/2014/04/02/how-did-stripe-come-up-with-its-name/|work = Forbes|accessdate = 2014-04-02|date = 2014-04-02|archive-date = 2014-04-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140406201458/http://www.forbes.com/sites/quora/2014/04/02/how-did-stripe-come-up-with-its-name/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2010年6月，Stripe由[[Y_Combinator_(公司)|Y Combinator]]獲得了種子基金<ref name="vb" />。2011年5月，Stripe由投資者[[彼得·泰爾|彼得·泰爾]]和投資公司[[紅杉資本|紅杉資本]]及{{le|安德森霍洛維茨|Andreessen Horowitz}}中取得了200萬美元<ref>{{cite web|last = Arrington|first = Michael|title = Stealth Payment Startup Stripe Backed By PayPal Founders|url = http://techcrunch.com/2011/03/28/stealth-payment-startup-stripe-paypal/|work = TechCrunch|accessdate = 2014-02-14|date = 2011-03-28|archive-date = 2014-02-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140210034817/http://techcrunch.com/2011/03/28/stealth-payment-startup-stripe-paypal/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2012年2月，Stripe在紅杉資本所帶領的一輪A系列投資中取得180萬美元，估值達一億美元<ref>{{cite web|last = Mitroff|first = Sarah|title = Stripe attracts $18M in funding at $100M valuation|url = http://venturebeat.com/2012/02/09/stripe-funding-valuation/|work = VentureBeat|accessdate = 2014-02-14|date = 2012-02-09|archive-date = 2014-02-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140210020232/http://venturebeat.com/2012/02/09/stripe-funding-valuation/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。Stripe在大規模的私人[[軟件版本週期|Beta測試]]後在2011年9月公開推出<ref>{{cite web|last = |first = |title = Stripe: instant payment processing for developers|url = https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=3053883|work = Hacker News|accessdate = 2014-02-14|date = 2011-09-29|archive-date = 2020-07-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200711112835/https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=3053883|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在公開推出後不足一年，Stripe便由{{le|General Catalyst Partners|General Catalyst Partners}}、紅杉資本、彼得·泰爾、{{le|Redpoint Ventures|Redpoint Ventures}}、[[克里斯·迪克森|克里斯·迪克森]]和[[亞倫·萊維|亞倫·萊維]]的B系列投資中取得二千萬美元投資<ref>{{cite web|last = Tsotsis|first = Alexia|title = Sexy Payments Startup Stripe Swipes $20M From General Catalyst, Sequoia, Thiel And More|url = http://techcrunch.com/2012/07/09/payments-startup-stripe-swipes-20m-from-general-catalyst-sequoia-thiel-and-more/|work = TechCrunch|accessdate = 2014-02-14|date = 2012-07-09|archive-date = 2014-02-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140216045212/http://techcrunch.com/2012/07/09/payments-startup-stripe-swipes-20m-from-general-catalyst-sequoia-thiel-and-more/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2013年3月，Stripe收購了{{le|任務管理|Task management}}程式Kickoff<ref>{{cite web|last=Rao|first=Leena|title=Payments Company Stripe Makes First Acquisition, Buys Team Task Management And Collaboration App Kickoff|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/03/11/payments-company-stripe-acquires-team-task-management-and-collaboration-app-kickoff/|work=TechCrunch|accessdate=2014-01-16|archive-date=2014-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113041525/http://techcrunch.com/2013/03/11/payments-company-stripe-acquires-team-task-management-and-collaboration-app-kickoff/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年3月，行政總裁帕特里克·科里森宣佈Stripe將會支援使用[[比特幣|比特幣]]付款<ref name="bitcoin">{{cite web|last = Del Rey|first = Jason|title = Stripe Merchants Will Soon Be Able to Accept Bitcoin Payments|url = http://recode.net/2014/03/27/stripe-merchants-will-soon-be-able-to-accept-bitcoin-payments/|work = Recode|accessdate = 2014-04-02|date = 2014-03-27|archive-date = 2014-03-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140330192524/http://recode.net/2014/03/27/stripe-merchants-will-soon-be-able-to-accept-bitcoin-payments/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 融资历史 == 

*2018年9月27日，E轮融资，Stripe获得 Tiger Global Management 领投，Sequoia Capital、Khosla Ventures、Thrive Capital和DST Global跟投的2.45亿美金投资。<ref name="stripehistory">{{Cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/stripe.html |title=互联网支付技术服务提供商：Stripe Inc. |publisher=美股之家 |date=2021-06-02 |access-date=2021-06-03 |archive-date=2021-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210603081854/https://www.mg21.com/stripe.html }}</ref>。
*2019年1月29日，E+轮融资，Stripe获得 Tiger Global Management 独家投资的1亿美金资金。
*2019年9月19日，G轮融资，Stripe获得 Andreessen Horowitz 和 General Catalyst领投，Sequoia Capital跟投的2.5亿美元投资。<ref name="stripehistory"/>
*2020年4月16日，G+轮融资，Sequoia Capital、Andreessen Horowitz、GV和General Catalyst共同投资了6亿美金。
*2020年5月28日，Stripe通过二级市场获得个人投资者Jean-Sébastien Wallez的投资。
*2021年3月14日，H轮融资，Stripe获得 Allianz X, AXA Group, Baillie Gifford, Fidelity Management and Research Company, National Treasury Management Agency (NTMA) 和 Sequoia Capital 共同投资的6亿美元资金。<ref name="stripehistory"/>

